summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the redevelopment proposal of Precision Builders, Inc. to purchase and develop Parcel 29C in the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (Wash. R-5) area; authorizing execution and delivery of contracts and deeds; authorizing the Director of Housing and Human Services to administer the Contract For Sale of Land; designating the disposition of sales proceeds; modifying the disposition procedures approved by Resolution 27260, and ratifying and confirming prior actions.
